    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不知何时，你在一片空地醒来，周围都是奇怪的空间扰动。你想不起来为什么会在这里，还好，你还记得你的名字。你潜意识里认为你来到这里是有一个非常重要的事情要做，但是，要做什么，你已经忘记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在你一筹莫展时，一袭白发的少女悄然走到你的面前，亲切地对你说……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款以装备构筑，角色养成为核心的Roguelike游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一点点的动作要素rogue+幸存者模式，指在前期构筑时更有选择的空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店购买提升能力的道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/efb6f008748eab7a1c18e2e9792b9bc0.avif?t=1763919017\" width=340 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有升级的基本三选一<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/c266e077b423c54352528a0ccbc2540b.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=440 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特殊的房间事件</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238250/extras_big/be5f6c2781f67847e1094239b2d4b424.avif?t=1763919017 width=800 height=406 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以，使用你的双手，拿起家伙，闯入奇异的世界，平息这里的混乱吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是不讲道理，挡在你面前的就是妖魔鬼怪，所以尽一切手段，取得胜利吧。</p>",
